---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Terms of Service" description="CalcBuild terms of service — usage terms and disclaimers.">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-6">Terms of Service</h1>
    <div class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed space-y-4">
      <p><strong class="text-slate-800">Last updated:</strong> May 2026</p>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-800 border-b-2 border-slate-200 pb-2 mb-4 mt-8">Disclaimer</h2>
      <p>The calculators and information provided on CalcBuild.online are for general informational purposes only. While we strive for accuracy, estimates may vary based on local conditions, material variations, and project specifics.</p>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-800 border-b-2 border-slate-200 pb-2 mb-4 mt-8">No Professional Advice</h2>
      <p>The results from our calculators should not be considered professional engineering or construction advice. Always consult with qualified professionals for your specific project requirements.</p>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-800 border-b-2 border-slate-200 pb-2 mb-4 mt-8">Use of Site</h2>
      <p>You may use CalcBuild for personal and commercial purposes. You may not redistribute, sell, or embed our calculators on other websites without written permission.</p>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-800 border-b-2 border-slate-200 pb-2 mb-4 mt-8">Contact</h2>
      <p>Questions about these terms? Visit our <a href="/contact/" class="text-primary-500 hover:text-primary-600 underline">contact page</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
